JSON Document Description:

theater_id | String | Unique identifier for each theater
name | String | Name of the theater
address | String | Address of the theater
contact_number | String | Contact number of the theater
layout | Object | Details of rows, columns, and seating sections of the theater
seating_info | Object Array | List of seats with location, availability and accessibility info

layout field:
rows | int | Number of rows in the theater
columns | int | Number of seats per row
special | Array | List of special seats (e.g., ADA-compliant)

seating_info field:
seat_id | String | Unique ID for the seat
row | int | Row number of the seat
column | int | Column number of the seat
is_available | boolean | Seat availability status 
is_accessible | boolean | indicates if the seat is ADA-compliant
